{"tid":1778063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿里巴巴馬雲、騰訊馬化騰、萬達王建林，下一個到順豐王衛","createTime":"2019-12-10T15:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T21:55:43.000Z","uid":31744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e32c9025ffa39eee1f43a810d11e7e1a82e615e","tid":1778063,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"王衛卸任順豐旗下商貿公司董事長<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體引述資料指，王衛卸任順豐控股(002352.SZ)旗下商貿有限公司董事長一職，由吳茜接任；而公司多位董事亦相繼退出。<br />\n<br />\n此外，元禾控股的投資實體之一蘇州工業園區元禾順風股權投資企業(有限合夥)、中信資本的投資實體之一嘉強順風(深圳)股權投資合夥企業(有限合夥)，以及古玉資本的投資實體之一蘇州古玉秋創股權投資合夥企業(有限合夥)，都退出投資人行列。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，王衛已卸任順豐控股的全資子公司順豐速運有限公司的法定代表人，董事長和執行董事，由陳雪穎接任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191210/mobile/bkn-20191210204635391-1210_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191210%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191210204635391-1210_00842_001.html&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=0c8f2a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191210/mobile/bkn-20191210204635391-1210_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國仲有冇有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fd0be66061990dd6356a022852e03c1466d141","tid":1778063,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:02:56.000Z","msg":"中國仲有冇有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daeb62fab3878d9e67630ada24b4bea48c578f7","tid":1778063,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"就算唔郁你,都整個黨委書記左右你"},{"pid":"bd1c16926acea6cf6e978299ef813c86637af9c2","tid":1778063,"uid":7206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"笑李嘉誠走早左果啲而家拎得返幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bc772d46140e5dcf15f65ca0